OL,5, A woman whose daughter missed out on a 
OL,6, free school bus by 0.1 miles has called
OL,7, the policy "a disgrace".               
OL,9,FBridgend council offers free transport 
OL,10,Fto primary school pupils who live more 
OL,11,Fthan two miles (3.2km) from school.    
OL,13,FBut Claire Jones, from Nantyfyllon, and
OL,14,Fher seven-year-old daughter, live 1.9  
OL,15,Fmiles from the school, meaning they are
OL,16,Fineligible for free bus travel.        
OL,18,FBridgend council said it has one of the
OL,19,Fmost generous travel policies in Wales 
OL,20,Fand met Welsh government requirements. 
